{
  "stem": "214.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had a beautiful voice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was always singing my Yiddish [INAUDIBLE] when we were working sometimes in the field.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were always [SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Are you crazy?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But-- but nobody-- nobody's-- those peasant women, they didn't really know very much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They just-- And-- and the doctors, the head doctors, Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Hauser, ?] He thought-- I don't know-- he knew that we are not-- so he thought that we may be in the Polish underground.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That we are-- somehow, we are not fitting in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and he was-- he was very-- but-- but he never said anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, he was an anti-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, when they would be all, Heil Hitler, he never would say Heil Hitler.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He always said [SPEAKING GERMAN] which means, you know, 'good afternoon,' or 'good  morning.'",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and-- and there it was lovely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only maybe the last night before the Americans came in, there was quite a bit of shooting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and then we got up in the morning, and the Americans were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we idiots thought that they would immediately know that we are somebody that they shouldn't shoot at.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were walking out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and then the big tank came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somebody took out a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, I don't know, probably in English, which we didn't understand-- if you don't turn back, I'm going to shoot.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't know-- [INAUDIBLE] especially, she thought they would take a look at her, and they would greet her with-- well, so that's how-- So how did you come to realize-- what happened at that moment?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If the Americans were there, how did they come to understand you were--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- the first-- the first thing which we did was, the next day, we didn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
